relevant_findings.oropharynx: Clear, without thrush or oral ulcerations
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm without murmurs, rubs, or gallops; pacemaker generator palpable without erythema, fluctuance, or tenderness
relevant_findings.abdomen: Soft and non-tender, normal bowel sounds, no hepatosplenomegaly
relevant_findings.lymphadenopathy: No palpable cervical, axillary, or inguinal lymphadenopathy

neurological.orientation: Oriented to person, place, and time
neurological.sensory_examination: Intact light touch and vibration; no saddle anesthesia, normal rectal tone
neurological.spine_examination: No point tenderness over any portion of spine or sacroiliac joints
neurological.straight_leg_raise: No radicular symptoms in either leg
neurological.bilateral_hip_exam: Normal flexion, internal rotation, and external rotation

relevant_findings.other_findings: No Janeway lesions or Osler nodes
